<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="offense-n">offense <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'fens/    美 /ə'fens/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-crime">1.★ <strong>[C] 违法行为；罪行 (crime)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>commit an <strong>offence against</strong> social order
犯妨害社会秩序罪</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 冒犯；侮辱：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t be upset by what he said; he <strong>meant no offense</strong>.
不要为他的话感到不快，他没有冒犯你的意思。</p></div></div>